@NoviCode.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5080

### 1) Create a player (201 Created + Location header)
POST {{NoviCode.Api_HostAddress}}/players
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "score": 100
}

### 2) List all players (200) — copy a player id from here for the wallet below.
GET {{NoviCode.Api_HostAddress}}/players

### 3) Get a player by id (200 or 404)
GET {{NoviCode.Api_HostAddress}}/players/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### 4) Create a wallet for a player (201 Created + Location header)
POST {{NoviCode.Api_HostAddress}}/wallets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "currency": "EUR"
}

### 5) Get a wallet by id — replace with the id returned above.
# First call = cache MISS (DB query), second call = cache HIT (no DB query — see the logs).
GET {{NoviCode.Api_HostAddress}}/wallets/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### 6) Get a non-existent wallet (404)
GET {{NoviCode.Api_HostAddress}}/wallets/99999999-9999-9999-9999-999999999999

### 7) Deposit into a wallet (200) — invalidates the cached entry.
POST {{NoviCode.Api_HostAddress}}/wallets/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50.00
}

### 8) Deposit a non-positive amount (400)
POST {{NoviCode.Api_HostAddress}}/wallets/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": -5
}
